  <p>Each Branch also contains <strong>hidden Stems</strong> (<span class="chinese-char">藏干</span>, Cánggān) &mdash; one to three elements concealed within. For example, the Horse branch (<span class="chinese-char">午</span>) contains Dīng Fire as its main element, plus Jǐ Earth. These hidden elements are critical in BaZi chart analysis, where they reveal deeper personality layers and latent potential.</p>
